    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nThe sign text and buffer text highlight attrs are not applied properly. Presumably because the refactor performed in #25826 makes wrong assumptions about an extmark that has both a buffer text hl group and sign text hl group attached to it.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n```vim\r\n\" test.vim\r\ncall setline(1, 'aaaa')\r\nlet ns = nvim_create_namespace('')\r\ncall nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, ns, 0, 0, {'sign_text':'S1','sign_hl_group':'Error','hl_group':'CursorLineNr','end_col':4})\r\n```\r\nRun `nvim --clean -S test.vim`\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nBoth the sign text and buffer text is highlighted as requested.\r\n\r\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\r\n\r\nNVIM v0.10.0-dev-1692+g79b6ff28a\r\n\r\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### Operating system/version\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### Terminal name/version\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### $TERM environment variable\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### Installation\r\n\r\nN/A",
